column5: Thank you Lord for taking the time to answer our prayers!
ouch...that's early. I'll check with the guy who's coming with me, maybe we'll see you there.
You got that right Cliff.. now if he will only answer for Jen.??? Hope he his listening,,,,,
Great News, Enjoy the show I'll be working SBK
As i said to you on the phone today Kelvin, i am so happy for both of you. You both deserve the break.
thats great! Any idea where people are getting together for breakfast? Doing Perkins like last time?
Thats great to hear Kelvin Shes a trooper
Thats great news Kelvin!
I think so it has a great breakfast
Kelvin, I'm really happy for BOTH of you! Great stuff! I know how much my Wife and best friend  means to me. I can't imagine going through something as scary as you both just did. Enjoy the show!
Thanks Guys ... she is a tough gal. Hell she has to be she's had me for 34 yrs now..  that what I will get if I'm not careful
Enjoy the time out Kelvin.... a well deserved break for BOTH of you!! lol  Glad she's done, hopefully for ever.
That is good news!
congrates !!!! great news indeed!
Good to hear!  See you Saturday!
Excellent news Kelvin.  Very happy for both of you!  Joey
That is great Kelvin!
Sweeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeet.
That is great news Kelvin!  Enjoy the show.
Thats excellent Kelvin! Great news for both of you.
Fantastic news Kelvin !!
Awesome news Kelvin very glad to here it. As for Breakfast I dont know if many or any are doing it now. If not there is always the show or afterwords for visiting.  See you Saturday for sure.
That is good news Kelvin, lets hope that's the end if it.
Thats awesome.
we will be at Perkins around 7.15 for breakfast... who wants to join us???
Thank YOU for the good news....this is twice this week I have heard GOOD NEWS.  Our family prayers are with you, Bob
Great News my friend !!!
